{"tid":1496980,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發，幫推！］發現港共政府好大執陰謀","createTime":"2019-08-22T18:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T07:07:12.000Z","uid":308692,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"552951471f764f43b3af715e2c9a214e63adb276","tid":1496980,"uid":308692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T18:15:02.000Z","msg":"<strong>首先，我為我嘅P牌感到抱歉</strong><br />\n<br />\n相信大家最近都發現中共/港共使用懷柔之術，希望令民眾發現和理非先係表達訴求嘅方法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">縱使大家都冇上當，但其實佢地已默默郁手，柔中帶強剛咁迫我地就犯</span><br />\n<br />\n首先係唔發不反對通知書<br />\n然後再唔比我地塞機場<br />\n呢個時候，又突然開始拉721嘅人，滿足下我地<br />\n有心理準備未來必定會係咁剛柔交接，收我地皮<br />\n再嚟就係9鐵事件<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">佢地嘅目的就係想平息一部分民憤，再set一條規矩，重覆一路壓落去直至我地再冇底牌，同時磨鳩我地意志，最後令整場運動收皮</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講咁多，都係要同大家講聲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">夠鐘set死線，勇武要回歸！<br />\n不割蓆，不分化！<br />\n呢個時候堆黑警極有可能又出懷柔之術，特登唔理，好似立法會嗰日咁俾我地衝，令勇武展示出「暴徒」姿態比人作新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個時候，前線手足大可以立即變返個和理非，你磨我又磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一齊磨到你鳩都爛</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命。兄弟爬山，各自努力。不割蓆，不分化。</span></span>"},{"pid":"8f852e46e0a8c95e49b5869e0a8cd17477532eb4","tid":1496980,"uid":308692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T18:19:49.000Z","msg":"唔好沉啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該幫推"},{"pid":"caa216d245a38d23a77e708183d7ba79b4ecaab8","tid":1496980,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa6dcf9e9162219774ba69b5c62f2b7cc008aa1","tid":1496980,"uid":263152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T18:47:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"76c9e256997b82f308586ecd940a7d0bd837f380","tid":1496980,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:07:12.000Z","msg":"香港電影欠香港人一場革命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497679\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497679</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZudLX07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZudLX07.jpg&h=5fb14145&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}